e":0},{"width":1600,"height":900,"file_path":"/5N2gd05TJ3oaas03PLuV4AG8MoD.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/vPKvMbQLEQGJIWNul6NTV1TBpNL.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/3om3vt1GC3hd5pOerSt9MC234f4.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/tCg2bpyeEuM6NJtWqEMTrwc974T.jpg","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/bAPyGicaAkQHYjnf0bHDppAJcWS.jpg","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/gwkVaizklNj2ml2glzHEFsFFL6S.jpg","iso_639_1":"ml","iso_3166_1":"IN","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/6mPS6x1ZnFKV1oSfVPGEzmXNGSf.jpg","iso_639_1":"ms","iso_3166_1":"MY","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/2OSiSq3aWfsq6TGYBqaeM5MHtTY.jpg","iso_639_1":"gl","iso_3166_1":"ES","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/khMeF54q1OVEZ5Ak387v0XiqZd5.jpg","iso_639_1":"eu","iso_3166_1":"ES","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/4W4SdxXqN9vSDmKORFu02QqrrVS.jpg","iso_639_1":"kn","iso_3166_1":"IN","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/86MN3UTrH38cx6fH26eb4YPmCnp.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/k6b2kHNA8loQcFX1hLmy0vg20cI.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/jWRh9LNv8SiY8pnGbNZIqJNyu0Z.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/sJPe6GjlxMXiaPJ7ytK2bSwDqKW.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-02-25T03:49:16.704+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"","runtime":120,"tagline":"Divididos por la familia. Impulsados ​​por el amor.","homepage":"","overview":"El amor entre Noah y Nick parece inquebrantable, a pesar de las maniobras de sus padres por separarles. Pero el trabajo de él y la entrada de ella en la universidad, abre sus vidas a nuevas relaciones. La aparición de una exnovia que busca venganza y de la madre Nick con intenciones poco claras, removerán los cimientos no solo de su relación, sino de la propia familia Leister. Cuando tantas personas están dispuestas a destruir una relación, ¿puede realmente acabar bien?"},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"È colpa tua?","runtime":121,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Noah deve lasciare la sua città, il fidanzato e gli amici per trasferirsi a casa del nuovo marito di sua madre. Lì conosce il fratellastro Nick e le loro personalità sono sin da subito in contrasto. Tuttavia, l'attrazione che provano li porterà a vivere una relazione proibita, in cui i caratteri ribelli e tormentati metteranno a soqquadro i rispettivi mondi, facendoli innamorare follemente."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"Your Fault","runtime":117,"tagline":"Divided by family. Driven by love.","homepage":"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0DJ1L7ZN3","overview":"The love between Noah and Nick seems unwavering despite their parents' attempts to separate them. But his job and her entry into college open up their lives to new relationships that will shake the foundations of both their relationship and the Leister family itself."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Sua Culpa","runtime":0,"tagline":"Separados pela família. Movidos pelo amor.","homepage":"","overview":"O amor entre Noah e Nick aparenta ser inabalável, apesar das tentativas de seus pais de separá-los. Mas o emprego dele, e a entrada dela na faculdade abrem suas vidas para novos relacionamentos. O retorno de uma ex-namorada vingativa e da mãe de Nick, com intenções obscuras, vão balançar não só o relacionamento deles, mas também de toda a família Leister. Quando tantas pessoas buscam destruir um relacionamento, será que ele consegue sobreviver?"},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"是你的错","runtime":120,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"全球热播电影《我的过错》续篇。尽管诺亚和尼克的父母试图拆散他们，但他们的关系似乎毫不动摇。然而他的工作和她的大学入学却给他们原本的生活带来了新的人际关系，眼看就要动摇他们的感情和莱斯特家族的根基。面对这么多蓄意破坏的人，这段感情真的能迎来圆满的结局吗？"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"À contre-sens 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"Divisés par la famille. Poussés par l'amour.","homepage":"https://www.primevideo.com/-/fr/detail/%C3%80-contre-sens-2/0G5EHVLC83CC57Z5DG60LLI69L","overview":"La relation entre Noah et Nick semble plus forte que jamais, malgré la volonté de leurs parents de les séparer. Mais avec son travail et son entrée à la fac, de nouvelles perspectives amoureuses feront trembler les fondations de leur relation et celles des Leister. Si tout le monde est prêt à détruire une relation, aura-t-on droit à une fin heureuse ?"},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Culpa Tuya - Deine Schuld","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Die Liebe zwischen Noah und Nick scheint unerschütterlich – trotz der Versuche ihrer Eltern, sie zu trennen. Aber sein Job und ihr Studienbeginn eröffnen neue Beziehungen, die ihre Liebe und die Familie Leister auf eine harte Probe stellen. Wenn so viele Menschen bereit sind, eine Beziehung zu zerstören, kann sie dann wirklich gut enden?"},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"אשמתך","runtime":120,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"למרות המאמצים של הוריהם להפריד ביניהם, אהבתם של נוח וניק נראית בלתי שבירה. עם זאת, העבודה והמכללה פותחות את חייהם למערכות יחסים חדשות."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Dünya çapında çok izlenen Culpa Mía'nın devam filmi olan bu filmde Noah ile Nick arasındaki aşk, ebeveynlerinin onları ayırmak için gösterdiği tüm çabalara rağmen sarsılmadan devam etmektedir. Ama Nick'in işi ve Noah'nın üniversiteye başlaması, ilişkilerinin ve Leister ailesinin temellerini sarsacak yeni ilişkilere kapı aralar. Bu kadar insanın yıkmaya çalıştığı bir ilişki ayakta kalabilir mi?"},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"Twoja wina","runtime":0,"tagline":"Podzieleni przez rodzinę. Kierowani miłością.","homepage":"","overview":"W wyczekiwanym sequelu międzynarodowego hitu \"Moja Wina\", namiętny romans Noah i Nicka staje przed nowymi wyzwaniami. Pomimo wysiłków rodziców, którzy starają się ich rozdzielić, ich miłość wydaje się nie do złamania. Jednak, gdy Nick poświęca się karierze, a Noah rozpoczyna studia, otwierają się przed nimi nowe znajomości i pojawiają się nowe pokusy. Wkraczając w dorosłość, doświadczają nowych wyzwań, a związek zostaje poddany ostatecznej próbie. Zewnętrzne siły zagrażają ich miłości, a reputacja ich rodzin wisi na włosku. Noah i Nick muszą walczyć mocniej niż kiedykolwiek, aby utrzymać swoją miłość przy życiu."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"შენი ბრალია","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"ქართული","iso_639_1":"ka","iso_3166_1":"GE","english_name":"Georgian"},{"data":{"title":"تو مقصری","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"عشق بین نوح و نیک علیرغم تلاش والدینشان برای جدایی‌شان تزلزل‌ناپذیر به‌نظر می‌رسد. اما شغل نیک و ورود نوح به دانشگاه، زندگی آن‌ها را به روی روابط جدیدی باز می‌کند که پایه‌های رابطه آن‌ها و خود خانواده لستر را متزلزل خواهد کرد."},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"你的過錯","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"全球熱門作品《我的過錯》續集，諾雅和尼可之間的愛情似乎堅不可摧，儘管他們的父母試圖將他們分開。然而，他的工作和她的大學生涯為他們的生活帶來了新的關係，這將撼動他們倆的情感和整個萊斯特家族的基礎。當這麼多人想要破壞一段感情時，它真的能有好結果嗎？"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Păcatul tău","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Urmarea succesului internațional „Păcatul meu”. Iubirea dintre Noah și Nick pare de neclintit, în ciuda încercărilor părinților de a-i despărți. Însă, după ce el se angajează, iar ea intră la facultate, în viața lor apar noi relații, care amenință temeliile relației lor și ale familiei Leister. Când atât de mulți oameni sunt gata să distrugă o relație, mai are aceasta sorți de izbândă?"},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"君の過ち","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"世界的ヒットとなった「俺の過ち」の続編。ノアとニックの関係は２人を引き離そうとする両親の意に反し、揺るぎないものになっている。しかしニックは法律事務所での研修、ノアは大学生活が始まり、それぞれに新しい出会いがある中で２人の関係やレイステル家の基礎が揺さぶられていく。大勢が壊そうとしている関係は本当にうまくいくのだろうか。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"คำขอโทษ 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ภาคต่อของคำขอโทษ ภาพยนตร์ที่ประสบความสำเร็จมาแล้วทั่วโลก ความรักระหว่างโนอาห์และนิคดูเหมือนจะมั่นคงไม่เปลี่ยนแปลง แม้ว่าพ่อแม่จะพยายามแยกทั้งสองออกจากกัน แต่หน้าที่การงานของนิคและการที่โนอาห์ได้เข้าเรียนในมหาวิทยาลัย เปิดโอกาสให้พวกเขาได้มีความสัมพันธ์ใหม่ๆ ที่จะสั่นคลอนรากฐานความสัมพันธ์ของพวกเขาและครอบครัวเลสเตอร์ เมื่อมีคนมากมายพร้อมจะทำลายความสัมพันธ์ ความสัมพันธ์นี้จะจบลงได้ดีจริงหรือไม่"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Culpa teva","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"En aquesta seqüela de la pel·lícula d'èxit Culpa meva, l'amor entre la Noah i en Nick sembla indestructible malgrat els intents dels seus pares de separar-los, però la feina i la universitat els posaran en situacions noves que sacsejaran les bases tant de la seva relació com de la mateixa família Leister. Quan tantes persones estan disposades a destruir una relació, realment pot acabar bé?"},"name":"Català","iso_639_1":"ca","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Catalan"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"Jaettu perheen mukaan. Rakkauden ajamana.","homepage":"","overview":"Noahin ja Nickin välinen rakkaus näyttää horjumattomalta, vaikka heidän vanhempansa yrittävät erottaa heidät toisistaan. Mutta Nickin työ ja Nickin pääsy yliopistoon avaavat heidän elämänsä uusille suhteille, jotka horjuttavat sekä heidän suhdettansa että koko Leisterin perheen perustaa."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"Твоята Вина","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Любовта между Ноа и Ник изглежда непоклатима въпреки опитите на родителите им да ги разделят. Но работата му и влизането й в колежа отварят живота им за нови взаимоотношения, които ще разклатят основите както на тяхната връзка, така и на самото семейство Листър."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"Tvoje vina","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Láska mezi Noah a Nickem se zdá neochvějná navzdory pokusům jejich rodičů oddělit je. Ale jeho práce a její nástup na vysokou školu otevírají jejich životy novým vztahům, které otřesou základy jak jejich vztahu, tak samotné rodiny Leisterů."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"네 잘못이야","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.primevideo.com/detail/0G5EHVLC83CC57Z5DG60LLI69L","overview":"전 세계적인 히트작 '나의 잘못'의 속편. 노아와 닉의 사랑은 둘을 떼어놓으려는 부모님의 노력에도 불구하고 흔들림이 없어 보인다. 하지만 닉의 직업과 노아의 대학 진학은 두 사람의 관계와 레이스테르 가족의 근간을 흔들 새로운 관계로 그들의 삶을 안내한다. 많은 사람이 두 사람 사이를 파괴하려는 가운데 이 둘은 결국 행복을 맞이할 수 있을까?"},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"\"Divided by family. Driven by love.\"","homepage":"","overview":"De liefde tussen Noah en Nick lijkt onwrikbaar, ondanks de pogingen van hun ouders om ze uit elkaar te halen. Maar zijn baan en haar toelating tot de universiteit openen hun levens voor nieuwe relaties die de fundamenten van zowel hun relatie als de familie Leister zelf zullen doen schudden."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"A te hibád","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"A világszerte sikeres Én vétkem folytatásában Noah és Nick szerelme megingathatatlannak tűnik, a szüleik hiába próbálják elválasztani őket egymástól. Ám a fiú munkája és a lány felvétele a főiskolára új fejezetet nyit a kapcsolatukban, és alapjaiban rázza meg nemcsak a viszonyukat, de a Leister családot is. Jól végződhet-e, ha ilyen sokan akarják tönkretenni a szerelmüket?"},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Culpa Tua","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"O amor de Noah e Nick parece sólido, apesar de os pais os tentarem separar. Mas o trabalho dele e a entrada dela para a faculdade abrem as suas vidas a novas relações que irão abalar os alicerces da sua relação e também da família Leister. Quando tanta gente se prepara para destruir uma relação, pode ela acabar bem?"},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"خطؤك","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"في تكملة لفيلم خطأي الذي حقق نجاحاً عالمياً، يبدو أن الحب بين نوا ونيك لا يتزعزع رغم محاولات والديهما التفريق بينهما. لكن عمله الجديد ودخولها إلى الكلية يفتحان حياتهما لعلاقات جديدة تهدد بزعزعة علاقتهما وعائلة ليستر بأكملها. عندما يكون هناك الكثير من الأشخاص المستعدين لتدمير العلاقة، هل يمكن حقاً أن يحظيا بنهاية سعيدة؟"},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"AE","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"خطؤك","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"في تكملة لفيلم خطأي الذي حقق نجاحاً عالمياً، يبدو أن الحب بين نوا ونيك لا يتزعزع رغم محاولات والديهما التفريق بينهما. لكن عمله الجديد ودخولها إلى الكلية يفتحان حياتهما لعلاقات جديدة تهدد بزعزعة علاقتهما وعائلة ليستر بأكملها. عندما يكون هناك الكثير من الأشخاص المستعدين لتدمير العلاقة، هل يمكن حقاً أن يحظيا بنهاية سعيدة؟"},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"Zure errua","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Mundu osoan arrakasta izan duen Nere Errua filmaren sekuela. Noahren eta Nicken arteko maitasunak hautsezina dirudi, gurasoak bikotea banantzen saiatu diren arren. Baina Nickek eta Noahk jende berria ezagutuko dute lanean eta unibertsitatean eta horrek arriskuan jarriko ditu haien harremana eta familia. Hainbeste jende harreman bat suntsitzeko prest dagoenean, aurkitu daiteke konponbiderik?"},"name":"euskera","iso_639_1":"eu","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Basque"},{"data":{"title":"是你的错","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"全球热播电影《我的过错》续篇。尽管诺亚和尼克的父母试图拆散他们，但他们的关系似乎毫不动摇。然而他的工作和她的大学入学却给他们原本的生活带来了新的人际关系，眼看就要动摇他们的感情和莱斯特家族的根基。面对这么多蓄意破坏的人，这段感情真的能迎来圆满的结局吗？"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"SG","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Culpa Tuya","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"I fortsættelsen til det globale hit Culpa Mía virker kærligheden mellem Noah og Nick urokkelig, selvom deres forældre gør alt for at adskille dem. Men hans nye job og hendes universitetsstudier bringer relationer ind i deres liv, som sætter deres forhold på prøve og ryster Leister-familien i sin grundvold. Kan deres forhold mon bestå, selvom så mange forsøger at forpurre det?"},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"À contre-sens 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"La vie amoureuse compliquée d'un jeune homme avec la fille de son riche nouveau beau-père."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Culpa túa","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Secuela do éxito mundial Culpa miña. O amor entre Noah e Nick semella inquebrantable, malia os intentos de separalos dos seus pais. Porén, o traballo del e a entrada na universidade dela ábrenlles as portas a novas relacións que sacudirán os cimentos da súa relación e da familia Leister. Cando tanta xente está disposta a destruír unha relación, pode acabar ben?"},"name":"Galego","iso_639_1":"gl","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Galician"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ένα σίκουελ της παγκόσμιας επιτυχίας Culpa Mía. Η αγάπη της Νόα και του Νικ μοιάζει ακλόνητη παρά τις προσπάθειες των γονιών τους να τους χωρίσουν. Αλλά η δουλειά του και οι σπουδές της τους οδηγούν σε νέες σχέσεις που θα ταρακουνήσουν τόσο τη σχέση τους όσο και την οικογένεια Λέιστερ. Όταν τόσοι άνθρωποι θέλουν να καταστρέψουν μια σχέση, μπορεί όντως να έχει αίσιο τέλος;"},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"यॉर फ़ॉल्ट","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"यह फ़िल्म ग्लोबल हिट माई फ़ॉल्ट का सीक्वेल है। नोआह और निक के माता-पिता के उन्हें अलग करने की लाख कोशिशों की बावजूद भी उनका प्यार अटूट है। पर निक की नौकरी और नोआ के नए कॉलेज में जाने के बाद उन्हें संबंध नए-लोगों से बनते हैं जिससे उनके अपने रिश्ते की नींव और ख़ुद लेस्टर परिवार भी हिल जाता है। क्यों इतने लोग एक रिश्ते को खत्म करना चाहते हैं, क्या सचमुच संबंध फिर से अच्छे होंगे?"},"name":"हिन्दी","iso_639_1":"hi","iso_3166_1":"IN","english_name":"Hindi"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Sekuel film laris My Fault; cinta Noah dan Nick tampak tak tergoyahkan meski orang tua berusaha memisahkan mereka. Namun, pekerjaan Noah dan masuknya Nick ke universitas membuka kehidupan baru yang akan mengguncang fondasi hubungan mereka dan keluarga Leister sendiri. Ketika begitu banyak orang siap menghancurkan suatu hubungan, dapatkah hubungan itu berakhir dengan baik?"},"name":"Bahasa indonesia","iso_639_1":"id","iso_3166_1":"ID","english_name":"Indonesian"},{"data":{"title":"ಯುವರ್ ಫಾಲ್ಟ್","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ಜಾಗತಿಕವಾಗಿ ಭರ್ಜರಿ ಯಶಸ್ಸು ಕಂಡ ಮೈ ಫಾಲ್ಟ್‌ನ ಮುಂದಿನ ಭಾಗ; ನೋವಾ ಮತ್ತು ನಿಕ್‌ರನ್ನು ಬೇರ್ಪಡಿಸಲು ಅವರ ಹೆತ್ತವರ ಪ್ರಯತ್ನಗಳ ಹೊರತಾಗಿಯೂ ಅವರ ಪ್ರೀತಿ ಅಚಲವಾಗಿದೆ. ಆದರೆ ಅವನ ಕೆಲಸ ಮತ್ತು ಅವಳ ಕಾಲೇಜು ಪ್ರವೇಶವು ಅವರ ಜೀವನದಲ್ಲಿ ಹೊಸ ಸಂಬಂಧಗಳನ್ನು ತರುತ್ತದೆ, ಇದು ಅವರ ಸಂಬಂಧ ಮತ್ತು ಲೈಸ್ಟರ್ ಕುಟುಂಬ ಎರಡರ ಅಡಿಪಾಯವನ್ನೂ ಅಲ್ಲಾಡಿಸುತ್ತದೆ. ಇಷ್ಟು ಜನರು ಸಂಬಂಧವನ್ನು ನಾಶಮಾಡಲು ಪ್ರಯತ್ನಿಸುತ್ತಿರುವಾಗ, ಅದು ನಿಜವಾಗಿಯೂ ಸುಖಾಂತ್ಯ ಕಾಣುವುದೇ?"},"name":"?????","iso_639_1":"kn","iso_3166_1":"IN","english_name":"Kannada"},{"data":{"title":"Kesalahanmu","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Sekuel kepada filem hit Kesalahanku ; cinta antara Noah dan Nick kekal utuh walaupun ibu bapa mereka cuba memisahkan. Namun, kerjaya Nick dan pengajian Noah menemukan mereka dengan perhubungan baharu yang bakal menggugat hubungan mereka dan keluarga Leister. Mampukah hubungan yang diancam dari segenap sudut itu bertahan?"},"name":"Bahasa melayu","iso_639_1":"ms","iso_3166_1":"MY","english_name":"Malay"},{"data":{"title":"യുവർ ഫോൾട്ട്","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ആഗോള ഹിറ്റായ മൈ ഫോൾട്ടിന്റെ തുടർച്ച; വേർപെടുത്താനുള്ള അച്ഛനമ്മമാരുടെ ശ്രമങ്ങൾക്കിടയിലും നോഹയുടെയും നിക്കിന്റെയും പ്രണയം അചഞ്ചലമായി നിൽക്കുന്നു. പക്ഷേ അവൻ്റെ ജോലിയും, അവളുടെ കോളേജ് പ്രവേശനവും അവരുടെ ജീവിതങ്ങളിലേക്ക് പുതിയ ബന്ധങ്ങൾ കൊണ്ടുവരുന്നു, അവരുടെ ബന്ധത്തെയും, ലെയ്സ്റ്റർ കുടുംബത്തെയും തന്നെ ഉലയ്ക്കുന്ന വിധത്തിൽ. ഒരുപാടുപേർ ഒരു ബന്ധം തകർക്കാൻ ശ്രമിക്കുമ്പോൾ അത് നല്ല രീതിയിൽ അവസാനിക്കുമോ?"},"name":"","iso_639_1":"ml","iso_3166_1":"IN","english_name":"Malayalam"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"En oppfølger til den globale hiten My Fault. Kjærligheten mellom Noah og Nick virker urokkelig på tross av foreldrenes forsøk på å skille dem. Men hans jobb og det at hun begynner å studere, åpner livene deres for mange nye forhold som vil ryste grunnlaget både for deres forhold og selve Leister-familien. Når så mange vil ødelegge et forhold, kan det virkelig ende bra?"},"name":"Norsk","iso_639_1":"no","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Uppföljaren till den globala succén Culpa Mía; kärleken mellan Noah och Nick verkar orubblig trots deras föräldrars försök att skilja dem åt. Men ett nytt jobb och college öppnar upp deras liv för nya relationer som kommer att försvåra situationen för deras förhållande och familjen Leister. När så många människor vill förstöra ett förhållande, kan det verkligen få ett lyckligt slut?"},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"யுவர் ஃபால்ட்","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"உலகளாவிய பிரபலமான மை ஃபால்ட் வெற்றிப் படத்தின் தொடர்ச்சி; நோவா, நிக் இடையிலான காதல், அவர்களது பெற்றோர் பிரிக்க முயல்வதையும் மீறி, கலைக்க முடியாததாகிறதோ? ஆனால், அவனது பணியும், அவள் புது கல்லூரியில் சேர்வதும் வாழ்வில் புதிய உறவுகளை துவக்கி, அவர்களது உறவு, லீஸ்டர் குடும்ப அடித்தளம் இரண்டையுமே கூட உலுக்கிவிடுகிறது. ஓர் உறவை பாழாக்க தயாராக இத்தனை பேர் இருக்கையில், இது உண்மையில் நல்லபடியாக முடியுமா?"},"name":"தமிழ்","iso_639_1":"ta","iso_3166_1":"IN","english_name":"Tamil"},{"data":{"title":"యువర్ ఫాల్ట్","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"గ్లోబల్ హిట్ మై ఫాల్ట్‌కి సీక్వెల్; నోవా, నిక్‌ల మధ్య ప్రేమ వారి తల్లిదండ్రులు వారిని వేరు చేయడానికి ప్రయత్నించినప్పటికీ అచంచలంగా ఉంది. కానీ అతని ఉద్యోగం, కళాశాలలో ఆమె ప్రవేశం వారి జీవితాలలో కొత్త సంబంధాలకు తెరతీస్తుంది, అది వారి సంబంధం మరియు లెస్టర్ కుటుంబం రెండింటి పునాదులను కదిలిస్తుంది. చాలా మంది వ్యక్తులు ఒక సంబంధాన్ని నాశనం చేయడానికి సిద్ధంగా ఉన్నప్పుడు, అది బాగా ముగుస్తుందా?"},"name":"తెలుగు","iso_639_1":"te","iso_3166_1":"IN","english_name":"Telugu"},{"data":{"title":"Твоя вина","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ноа и Николас влюблены и счастливы, но это прекрасное чувство очень хрупко. Достаточно одной искры, чтобы пламя недоверия все разрушило. Смогут ли влюбленные преодолеть попытки родителей их разлучить? Удастся ли им сохранить чувства, несмотря на появление бывшей девушки Ника, новых друзей Ноа из колледжа и другие испытания?"},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"A pesar de los esfuerzos de sus padres por separarlos, el amor de Noah y Nick parece inquebrantable. Sin embargo, el trabajo y la universidad abren sus vidas a nuevas experiencias. Además, la aparición de una exnovia que busca venganza removerá los cimientos de su relación."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Твоя провина","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Кохання Ноа і Ніка здається непохитним, незважаючи на спроби їхніх батьків розлучити їх. Але його робота і її вступ до коледжу відкривають їхні життя для нових відносин, які похитнуть основи як їхніх стосунків, так і самої сім'ї Лейстерів."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"Tavo kaltė","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Meilė tarp Nojos ir Niko tvirta, nepaisant jų tėvų bandymų juos atskirti. Tačiau jo naujasis darbas ir jos įstojimas į koledžą atveria jų gyvenimus naujiems santykiams, kurie supurtys ne tik jų santykių, bet ir pačios Leisterių šeimos pamatus."},"name":"Lietuvių","iso_639_1":"lt","iso_3166_1":"LT","english_name":"Lithuanian"},{"data":{"title":"你的過錯","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"全球熱門作品《我的過錯》續集，諾雅和尼可之間的愛情似乎堅不可摧，儘管他們的父母試圖將他們分開。然而，他的工作和她的大學生涯為他們的生活帶來了新的關係，這將撼動他們倆的情感和整個萊斯特家族的基礎。當這麼多人想要破壞一段感情時，它真的能有好結果嗎？"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Tvoja krivda","runtime":0,"tagline":"Ločena zaradi družine. Povezana z ljubeznijo.","homepage":"","overview":"Ljubezen med Noah in Nickom se zdi neomajna, kljub poskusom njunih staršev, da bi ju ločili. Toda njegova zaposlitev in njen vstop na fakulteto odpreta vrata novim poznanstvom, ki zamajejo temelje njunega razmerja - in družine Leister kot celote."},"name":"Slovenščina","iso_639_1":"sl","iso_3166_1":"SI","english_name":"Slovenian"},{"data":{"title":"Lỗi Tại Anh","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Tình yêu giữa Noah và Nick tưởng chừng là bất diệt, bất chấp mọi nỗ lực chia cắt từ phía cha mẹ. Thế nhưng, khi Nick bắt đầu guồng quay công việc còn Noah bước chân vào cánh cửa đại học, cuộc sống của cả hai dần mở ra những mối quan hệ mới. Chính những nhân tố mới này sẽ làm lung lay tận gốc rễ niềm tin giữa họ, đồng thời khiến cả gia tộc Leister một lần nữa chao đảo"},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":1294203,"adult":false,"title":"My Fault: London","video":false,"overview":"18-year-old Noah moves from America to London, with her mother who's recently fallen in love with William, a wealthy British businessman. Noah meets William’s son, bad-boy Nick, and soon discovers there is an attraction between them neither can avoid. As Noah spends the summer adjusting to her new life, her devastating past will catch up with her while falling in love for the first time.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":9.196,"vote_count":529,"poster_path":"/ttN5D6GKOwKWHmCzDGctAvaNMAi.jpg","release_date":"2025-02-12","vote_average":7.407,"backdrop_path":"/uJK0jjJ8QDOQw5lcNBwu059ht4D.jpg","original_title":"My Fault: London","original_language":"en"},{"id":1010581,"adult":false,"title":"My Fault","video":false,"overview":"Noah must leave her city, boyfriend, and friends to move into William Leister's mansion, the flashy and wealthy husband of her mother Rafaela. As a proud and independent 17 year old, Noah resists living in a mansion surrounded by luxury. However, it is there where she meets Nick, her new stepbrother, and the clash of their strong personalities becomes evident from the very beginning.","genre_ids":[18,10749,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":29.1786,"vote_count":3998,"poster_path":"/w46Vw536HwNnEzOa7J24YH9DPRS.jpg","release_date":"2023-06-08","vote_average":7.763,"backdrop_path":"/oz4U9eA6ilYf1tyiVuGmkftdLac.jpg","original_title":"Culpa mía","original_language":"es"},{"id":1252309,"adult":false,"title":"Tell Me What You Want","video":false,"overview":"After his father's death, Eric Zimmerman travels to Spain to oversee his company's branches. In Madrid, he falls for Judith and engage in an intense, erotic relationship full of exploration. However, Eric fears his secret may end their affair.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":12.7566,"vote_count":268,"poster_path":"/yZXYCiZQPB7Ui6D5206W1zDKv8P.jpg","release_date":"2024-11-29","vote_average":6.131,"backdrop_path":"/8Rseq6hAhAItnTrbECEFt35VoSJ.jpg","original_title":"Pídeme lo que quieras","original_language":"es"},{"id":845781,"adult":false,"title":"Red One","video":false,"overview":"After Santa Claus (codename: Red One) is kidnapped, the North Pole's Head of Security must team up with the world's most infamous tracker in a globe-trotting, action-packed mission to save Christmas.","genre_ids":[28,35,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":10.8537,"vote_count":2944,"poster_path":"/cdqLnri3NEGcmfnqwk2TSIYtddg.jpg","release_date":"2024-10-31","vote_average":6.999,"backdrop_path":"/rOmUuQEZfPXglwFs5ELLLUDKodL.jpg","original_title":"Red One","original_language":"en"},{"id":1255788,"adult":false,"title":"The Gardener","video":false,"overview":"Every year the Prime Minister has a list of all kinds of troublemakers eliminated in the name of the famous Reason of State. Serge Shuster, Special Adviser to the President of the Republic, finds himself on this list, better known as the Matignon List.  Condemned to certain death and at the heart of an implacable plot and a state secret that also put his family in danger, Serge, his wife and children have only one hope left - their gardener, Léo, who hates it when « slugs » invade his garden... Especially those that want to kill innocent families.","genre_ids":[28,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.6595,"vote_count":179,"poster_path":"/5T9WR7vIOnHm6xhVt5zBuPbBgt1.jpg","release_date":"2025-01-30","vote_average":6.078,"backdrop_path":"/HGmX2QmO1a67a1awAfHFEnDCiF.jpg","original_title":"Le Jardinier","original_language":"fr"},{"id":939243,"adult":false,"title":"Sonic the Hedgehog 3","video":false,"overview":"Sonic, Knuckles, and Tails reunite against a powerful new adversary, Shadow, a mysterious villain with powers unlike anything they have faced before. With their abilities outmatched in every way, Team Sonic must seek out an unlikely alliance in hopes of stopping Shadow and protecting the planet.","genre_ids":[28,878,35,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":18.0901,"vote_count":3145,"poster_path":"/d8Ryb8AunYAuycVKDp5HpdWPKgC.jpg","release_date":"2024-12-19","vote_average":7.625,"backdrop_path":"/noPEm6Vu9Lm6QUdTGLOyRgk4M6s.jpg","original_title":"Sonic the Hedgehog 3","original_language":"en"},{"id":219173,"adult":false,"title":"It's Your Fault","video":false,"overview":"Are we what others see, or are we what we allow others to see? Most likely it is the view of others which delimits our own identity, as a young divorced mother named Julieta convinces herself. This evening is like any other: her two young sons are roughhousing in their cramped apartment. They whoop and shout while their mother makes desperately futile attempts at the computer to concentrate on writing a report for work. Feeling intense pressure, Julieta tries to quiet the conflict but finds it difficult without a partner to help. The tense situation changes unexpectedly when her two-year-old falls and hurts himself. In this story of a mother suspected of hurting her own child, the movie investigates themes of motherhood, guilt, duty, the role of men and women, fathers and mothers","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1761,"vote_count":8,"poster_path":"/adq0PXI1k8EVJD6l6XaC4z5iLNe.jpg","release_date":"2010-06-02","vote_average":6.4,"backdrop_path":"/rfG5iZD7vMq3tgbpG3oOjoZIcLU.jpg","original_title":"Por tu culpa","original_language":"es"},{"id":558449,"adult":false,"title":"Gladiator II","video":false,"overview":"Years after witnessing the death of the revered hero Maximus at the hands of his uncle, Lucius is forced to enter the Colosseum after his home is conquered by the tyrannical Emperors who now lead Rome with an iron fist. With rage in his heart and the future of the Empire at stake, Lucius must look to his past to find strength and honor to return the glory of Rome to its people.","genre_ids":[28,12,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":12.0988,"vote_count":4205,"poster_path":"/2cxhvwyEwRlysAmRH4iodkvo0z5.jpg","release_date":"2024-11-13","vote_average":6.631,"backdrop_path":"/4hvK1uenpT7VVClzoNqXanvgdjX.jpg","original_title":"Gladiator II","original_language":"en"},{"id":957119,"adult":false,"title":"Sidelined: The QB and Me","video":false,"overview":"Dallas, a burdened but headstrong dancer, is determined to get into the best dance school in the country—her late mother’s alma mater. However, that dream is suddenly derailed when the cheeky yet secretly grieving football star, Drayton, crashes into her life with a unique story of his own. Will the two of them be able to grow into their dreams together, or will their dreams be sidelined?","genre_ids":[35,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":15.0304,"vote_count":180,"poster_path":"/mSL6truNrWP1Bn9ng1rN0SkMI4f.jpg","release_date":"2025-02-06","vote_average":6.158,"backdrop_path":"/wbDkvShcrveXNFsgyujY4kdurVa.jpg","original_title":"Sidelined: The QB and Me","original_language":"en"},{"id":1209450,"adult":false,"title":"National Family","video":false,"overview":"Don Poli, the patriarch of a family embedded in politics, faces the change of party in his state - after a hundred years in power - losing all his privileges. Humiliated and angry, he threatens to disinherit his family and leave to rebuild his life. This forces his children (Kippy, Ramses and Belén) to take extreme measures to ensure their future, causing everything that could go wrong to turn out worse.","genre_ids":[35,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3595,"vote_count":90,"poster_path":"/oSAzrJ0AjFZLUCcHT8YAnuD7egp.jpg","release_date":"2023-12-28","vote_average":6.7,"backdrop_path":"/2qaFnZxMkj5nKz1MWinaVNfg7T7.jpg","original_title":"Familia Nacional","original_language":"es"},{"id":779816,"adult":false,"title":"White Bird","video":false,"overview":"After being expelled from Beecher Prep for his treatment of a classmate with a facial deformity, Julian has struggled to fit in at his new school. To transform his life, Julian's grandmother finally reveals her own story of courage of her youth in Nazi-occupied France, where a classmate shelters her from mortal danger.","genre_ids":[18,10752],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.6889,"vote_count":226,"poster_path":"/s2igE99PVBEMsry3qEGEH3rM83K.jpg","release_date":"2023-10-25","vote_average":7.841,"backdrop_path":"/l7U8hKJsDL2DfYg7nYUACewg9d0.jpg","original_title":"White Bird","original_language":"en"},{"id":839033,"adult":false,"title":"The Lord of the Rings: The War of the Rohirrim","video":false,"overview":"A sudden attack by Wulf, a clever and traitorous lord of Rohan