fering from a forbidden love.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":0.132,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/4pRq4XcqkiuxjUmBD9TcjK7nZ9D.jpg","release_date":"1956-01-01","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Ölmüş Bir Kadının Evrak-ı Metrukesi","original_language":"tr"},{"id":70,"adult":false,"title":"Million Dollar Baby","video":false,"overview":"Despondent over a painful estrangement from his daughter, trainer Frankie Dunn isn't prepared for boxer Maggie Fitzgerald to enter his life. But Maggie's determined to go pro and to convince Dunn and his cohort to help her.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":5.5225,"vote_count":10183,"poster_path":"/jcfEqKdWF1zeyvECPqp3mkWLct2.jpg","release_date":"2004-12-05","vote_average":7.954,"backdrop_path":"/oGMomeS7bE43eN8SGJUaKvQnmud.jpg","original_title":"Million Dollar Baby","original_language":"en"},{"id":78,"adult":false,"title":"Blade Runner","video":false,"overview":"In the smog-choked dystopian Los Angeles of 2019, blade runner Rick Deckard is called out of retirement to terminate a quartet of replicants who have escaped to Earth seeking their creator for a way to extend their short life spans.","genre_ids":[878,18,53],"popularity":11.9762,"vote_count":14713,"poster_path":"/63N9uy8nd9j7Eog2axPQ8lbr3Wj.jpg","release_date":"1982-06-25","vote_average":7.9,"backdrop_path":"/hJ5R9d6QuH3tzr8L8neZZTuzNXm.jpg","original_title":"Blade Runner","original_language":"en"},{"id":86,"adult":false,"title":"The Elementary Particles","video":false,"overview":"Based on Michel Houellebecq's controversial novel, Atomised (aka The Elementary Particles) focuses on Michael and Bruno, two very different half-brothers and their disturbed sexuality.  After a chaotic childhood with a hippie mother only caring for her affairs, Michael, a molecular biologist, is more interested in genes than women, while Bruno is obsessed with his sexual desires, but mostly finds his satisfaction with prostitutes.  But Bruno's life changes when he gets to know the experienced Christiane.  In the meantime, Michael meets Annabelle, the love of his youth, again.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":0.6159,"vote_count":146,"poster_path":"/wpGpR7GewyApPgqPvuWadBAfmFc.jpg","release_date":"2006-02-10","vote_average":6.12,"backdrop_path":"/60PJPzXtQmLQdaCNuWUrrHe1mzu.jpg","original_title":"Elementarteilchen","original_language":"de"},{"id":653824,"adult":false,"title":"Casa din vis","video":false,"overview":"Căpălău, a peasant in a village near Brăila, tries to keep up with the turns of life. Based on \"Ningea în Bărăgan” novel by Fănuș Neagu.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.1702,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"1992-01-13","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Casa din vis","original_language":"ro"},{"id":854152,"adult":false,"title":"Inubu: The Dog Club","video":false,"overview":"Hanai Sota is 22-years-old and a university student in the veterinary department. Since he was little, he has always loved animals. His apartment is full of animals that needed help. One day, Hanai Sota saves a dog that was being used in experiments. To save more of the animals, he sets up the \"Inubu\" club. His friend Shibasaki Ryosuke, among other people, joins the group. Shibasaki Ryosuke also loves dogs and is a student in the same veterinary department as Hanai Sota. They work hard to protect the animals. 16 years later, a report comes out. The report is about Hanai Sota, who was arrested.","genre_ids":[18,10751],"popularity":0.4795,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/982Vb7oAw6CWacnKbDjzan7QKIU.jpg","release_date":"2021-07-22","vote_average":6.75,"backdrop_path":"/nvOrS60C5x3pL4aAY5hlT7S6jY7.jpg","original_title":"犬部！","original_language":"ja"},{"id":13,"adult":false,"title":"Forrest Gump","video":false,"overview":"A man with a low IQ has accomplished great things in his life and been present during significant historic events—in each case, far exceeding what anyone imagined he could do. But despite all he has achieved, his one true love eludes him.","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"popularity":20.2801,"vote_count":29286,"poster_path":"/saHP97rTPS5eLmrLQEcANmKrsFl.jpg","release_date":"1994-06-23","vote_average":8.462,"backdrop_path":"/67HggiWaP9ZLv5sPYmyRV37yAJM.jpg","original_title":"Forrest Gump","original_language":"en"},{"id":854024,"adult":false,"title":"Netrpezlivosť srdca","video":false,"overview":"A TV adaptation of a novel by Austrian writer Stefan Zweig. The tragic love story of a lame girl and a lieutenant provides a framework for reflection on human compassion. A young officer wants to gain status and is looking for a \"good match.\" He insinuates himself into the home of a local wealthy man, partly because he loves his niece. Under unfortunate circumstances, he discovers that the wealthy man's daughter has been paralyzed from the waist down for some time. She takes the officer's apologies and frequent visits as a sign of affection. She believes him and begins to hope again that she will recover. This is also so that she can be an equal partner to him, like other women. At first, the officer plays along.","genre_ids":[18,10770],"popularity":0.1266,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"1974-01-01","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Netrpezlivosť srdca","original_language":"sk"},{"id":271185,"adult":false,"title":"Ask Me Anything","video":false,"overview":"Beautiful, wild, funny, and lost, Katie Kampenfelt takes a year off before college to find herself, all the while chronicling her adventures in an anonymous blog into which she pours her innermost secrets. Eventually, Katie's fearless narrative begins to crack, and dark pieces of her past emerge.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":1.3162,"vote_count":422,"poster_path":"/u0rEtOp6jI7oU6u3m7v1aAOJNQr.jpg","release_date":"2014-04-19","vote_average":5.6,"backdrop_path":"/4v7osWGP3caNCth0g2boIWEJNqY.jpg","original_title":"Ask Me Anything","original_language":"en"},{"id":271218,"adult":false,"title":"The Sob","video":false,"overview":"After his mother had died, Kenan (Muzaffer Tema) left the home to take care of a goodhearted rich man, whose daughter Nalan (Nedret Güvenç) fell deeply in love with him...","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":1.264,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/8aHiTlq4CXZ0JcaOxRwTYiBYtLn.jpg","release_date":"1953-01-01","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Hıçkırık","original_language":"tr"},{"id":270918,"adult":false,"title":"Tricycle","video":false,"overview":"Üç tekerlekli bisiklet (Tricycle aka The Three-Wheeled Bicycle, I962) is a love story about a lonely woman with a small child and the man she hides in her house, who is chased and trapped, one of the staple motifs of Lutfi Akad’s cinema.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.1604,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/7SlaRmAixlsaOIWukD0dMb3x9Xu.jpg","release_date":"1962-01-02","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/8z6X1dETzrnrQqhnEkW1EoyAAyg.jpg","original_title":"Üç Tekerlekli Bisiklet","original_language":"tr"},{"id":1452237,"adult":false,"title":"Lügen über meine Mutter","video":false,"overview":"In the 1980s, the life of a family in a small village is determined by just one issue: the mother's body weight. Her husband Werner decides that she needs to lose weight, Cornelia suffers as a result and their daughter Ela is caught in the middle.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.1824,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Lügen über meine Mutter","original_language":"de"},{"id":1587,"adult":false,"title":"What's Eating Gilbert Grape","video":false,"overview":"Gilbert Grape is a small-town young man with a lot of responsibility. Chief among his concerns are his mother, who is so overweight that she can't leave the house, and his mentally impaired younger brother, Arnie, who has a knack for finding trouble. Settled into a job at a grocery store and an ongoing affair with local woman Betty Carver, Gilbert finally has his life shaken up by the free-spirited Becky.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"popularity":4.457,"vote_count":4198,"poster_path":"/8FxWgsfDNosewo7H65oE4QkOb7g.jpg","release_date":"1993-12-17","vote_average":7.662,"backdrop_path":"/fHuKwcrwltGlWn3510N1YO7vJ4I.jpg","original_title":"What's Eating Gilbert Grape","original_language":"en"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt28510079","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q128787041","instagram_id":null,"rotten_tomatoes_id":"m/culpa_tuya"},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":148277,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"AR","release_dates":[{"note":"Prime Video","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2024-12-27T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"AS","release_dates":[{"note":"Prime Video","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2024-12-26T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"AT","release_dates":[{"note":"Prime Video","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2024-12-27T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"BE","release_dates":[{"note":"Prime Video","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2024-12-27T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"BG","release_dates":[{"note":"Prime Video","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2024-12-27T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"BO","release_dates":[{"note":"Prime Video","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2024-12-27T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","release_dates":[{"note":"Prime Video","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":["Sexual Content","Illegal Drugs"],"release_date":"2024-12-26T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"18"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"CA","release_dates":[{"note